  "name": "RPlog_Caspar_s_Good_Faith",
  "title": "A Good-Faith Bargain at the Imperial Embassy",
  "summary": "With Corellia locked down and the galaxy on edge after the escape of two CDU ambassadors from the HIMS Inquisitor, Admiral Naten Bonrue, head of the Caspian Naval Intelligence Office, comes to the Imperial Embassy on Caspar to head off a slide toward war. He meets ISB Station Chief Commander Zyar, who frostily lays out the Empire's case: Ambassadors Dareus and Quinn were detained over links to the Maffi crime syndicate, then sprung in what the Empire deems an act of sedition. To prove the CDU's good faith and distance itself from the fugitives, Bonrue hands over intelligence naming the Twi'lek Tyy'sun Eson as Maffi's leader and Gren Delede's CSA vessel Litigator as the Resistance flagship. Zyar accepts the gesture but warns that harboring the war criminals would itself be an act of war, and the tense meeting ends with the CDU delegation escorted out.",
